  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A game of dreams about games.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on Overlook Trail, a mixtape of arcade gameplay, 3D platforming, and peculiar puzzles. Navigate through surreal landscapes with ever-changing challenges.<br><strong></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/11f2996d56c9585d681688e27ded9a08.poster.avif?t=1757681107\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/11f2996d56c9585d681688e27ded9a08.webm?t=1757681107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/11f2996d56c9585d681688e27ded9a08.mp4?t=1757681107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Dreamlike flying on a leaf, try to get to your destination without crashing or dropping to the ground. Fly through rings to collect more fuel and collect orbs for a better score.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/1992b88bebdde6059cc1fc32cce19c1d.poster.avif?t=1757681107\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/1992b88bebdde6059cc1fc32cce19c1d.webm?t=1757681107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/1992b88bebdde6059cc1fc32cce19c1d.mp4?t=1757681107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Surreal foodscape racing level, where you must overtake orbs and dodge obstacles, such as jelly doughnuts, banana dolphins, and a nasty toaster oven.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/551328bac831ba75a6582b2ba44ab9d1.poster.avif?t=1757681107\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/551328bac831ba75a6582b2ba44ab9d1.webm?t=1757681107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/551328bac831ba75a6582b2ba44ab9d1.mp4?t=1757681107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Space themed on-rails level with arcade-style gameplay.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/ab1804b3c9d9aed479aaac374f690bff.poster.avif?t=1757681107\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/ab1804b3c9d9aed479aaac374f690bff.webm?t=1757681107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/ab1804b3c9d9aed479aaac374f690bff.mp4?t=1757681107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Goofy environments with quirky puzzles.</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A game of dreams about games.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on Overlook Trail, a mixtape of arcade gameplay, 3D platforming, and peculiar puzzles. Navigate through surreal landscapes with ever-changing challenges.<br><strong></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/11f2996d56c9585d681688e27ded9a08.poster.avif?t=1757681107\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/11f2996d56c9585d681688e27ded9a08.webm?t=1757681107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/11f2996d56c9585d681688e27ded9a08.mp4?t=1757681107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Dreamlike flying on a leaf, try to get to your destination without crashing or dropping to the ground. Fly through rings to collect more fuel and collect orbs for a better score.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/1992b88bebdde6059cc1fc32cce19c1d.poster.avif?t=1757681107\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/1992b88bebdde6059cc1fc32cce19c1d.webm?t=1757681107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/1992b88bebdde6059cc1fc32cce19c1d.mp4?t=1757681107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Surreal foodscape racing level, where you must overtake orbs and dodge obstacles, such as jelly doughnuts, banana dolphins, and a nasty toaster oven.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/551328bac831ba75a6582b2ba44ab9d1.poster.avif?t=1757681107\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/551328bac831ba75a6582b2ba44ab9d1.webm?t=1757681107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/551328bac831ba75a6582b2ba44ab9d1.mp4?t=1757681107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Space themed on-rails level with arcade-style gameplay.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/ab1804b3c9d9aed479aaac374f690bff.poster.avif?t=1757681107\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/ab1804b3c9d9aed479aaac374f690bff.webm?t=1757681107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817800/extras/ab1804b3c9d9aed479aaac374f690bff.mp4?t=1757681107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Goofy environments with quirky puzzles.</i></p>",
